main event: A sighting of one than three round objects resembling automobile headlights near McChord AFB on April 18, 1956.
interesting points: The objects were described as being white in color,The sighting lasted for 3 hours,The objects appeared to block distance and were seen simultaneously from different locations,Initial conclusions varied from balloon to aircraft,There were reports of a CL-24 aircraft making landing patterns at the time of the sighting.
sighted object: one than three round objects similar to automobile headlights
